longBusinessSummary: Ecrid, Inc. offers services in the credit repair industry. It provides up to date credit report services to lenders through its credit monitoring software. The company was formerly known as dPollution International Inc. Ecrid, Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Stuart, Florida.
